<plot>'Wise old little boy' is an intimate portrait of Phil Elverum (the microphones) and Kyle Field (little wings). joining their tour of small towns and unconventional venues, filmmaker Ryer Banta explores the world of two incredibly unique and creative musicians. This documentary captures numerous live performances, conversations, and other revealing moments from their 'wise old little boy' tour.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?658729</url></doc>
